fr.jgetmove.jgetmove.database

Class Base

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.jgetmove.jgetmove.database.Base
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrettyPrint
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataBase

    public class Base
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrettyPrint
    Class containing all the basic data.

    All the data is binded once, note that adding or rebinding data in here is expensive. Use ClusterMatrix for a dynamic database.

    Since:
    0.2.0
    See Also:
    ClusterMatrix
